{"tid":2199345,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"遭網友狠批「漢奸崇美」　美華裔作家：被中國利用作政治宣傳","createTime":"2020-09-12T06:31:46.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-12T09:55:07.000Z","uid":240362,"like":24,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"e83d7ddd84c9da7f2a1af7f1b7731e84babc0c9d","tid":2199345,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-12T06:31:46.000Z","msg":"美籍華裔作家樊嘉揚（Jiayang Fan）早前透過推特，向醫院爭取豁免權，讓私人護理得以在疫情期間留院照料患上漸凍人症（ALS）的母親。事件在中國被廣為報道和發酵，樊嘉揚更成為中國網友圍攻的目標，被批評是「叛徒」、「崇美」、令「家族蒙羞」。她在《紐約客》（New Yorker）雜誌撰文，剖白自己和母親被中國利用作政治宣傳的經過。<br />\n<br />\n樊嘉揚文章題為《我和母親如何成為中國的政治宣傳工具》（How My Mother and I Became Chinese Propaganda），她表示，自己1984年生於中國重慶，兩歲時父親獲派美國哈佛大學留學，修讀生物學；8歲時，她跟隨做醫生的母親赴美，與父親團聚。<br />\n<br />\n樊嘉揚的遭遇很快在中國被廣為報導。黨媒《環球時報》指，樊嘉揚去年為《紐約客》到香港採訪抗爭運動時，遭示威者針對，事後在推特形容自己中國人面孔是「累贅」。其他報導指，她的文章支持香港民主運動，「錯誤指控新冠病毒的發源地是中國」，結果樊嘉揚遭到大量中國網友惡意攻擊，在微信、推特、臉書、Instagram等平台圍攻，批評她是叛徒，靠誹謗祖國維生，咒駡她「NMSL」（「你媽死了」），更恐嚇要燒死、強姦、虐待她。樊嘉揚和母親的照片，也在中國網路被瘋傳，一名叫「China15z0dj」的網友留言說：「你媽將會死，哈哈。14億人民也祝你下地獄和她團聚，哈哈。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/international/20200912/O4OQFKRBSBDIZGTU4SGHREXDM4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20200912%2FO4OQFKRBSBDIZGTU4SGHREXDM4%2F&d=D4HIriwr0d5ovb2eA4y9f%2FCGrV5sAEOTHy2vWGvapoA%3D&h=3e703205\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20200912%2FO4OQFKRBSBDIZGTU4SGHREXDM4%2F&h=d48ffb14\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://tw.appledaily.com/international/20200912/O4OQFKRBSBDIZGTU4SGHREXDM4/</a>"},{"pid":"1ef8a39ebb2bc1b9fcf56418215f5e4150a7542e","tid":2199345,"uid":240362,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-12T06:32:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/resizer/ak5X0Eo7CP8cOfloAP6gJrQHnuw=/760x576/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/JZZI2FFXH5F6BCMNTPGC2G2XFA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Fak5X0Eo7CP8cOfloAP6gJrQHnuw%3D%2F760x576%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FJZZI2FFXH5F6BCMNTPGC2G2XFA.jpg&h=8d75277f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n樊嘉揚一直有關注香港情況，今年維園六四晚會不獲准舉行，她認為疫情可能是考慮因素之一，但不能假裝這是唯一原因。"},{"pid":"85e11cb1ddeab4aaf7c033817c93485ee280d615","tid":2199345,"uid":312333,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-12T06:35:27.000Z","msg":"被中國人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"93177df06cf95bb60c30be2773ebc92d4f5ee366","tid":2199345,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-12T06:35:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2bef2611cfdede0ef996ebcee4e5695b347e45c8","tid":2199345,"uid":10757,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-12T06:37:49.000Z","msg":"中國人就係 好似差佢錢咁 總知中國黎你就唔講得壞話 講左你就係漢奸 最鍾意意認親認戚 早10代溝左中國種都要講出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"295ad5d85fade7d6f2c65f87d8f50420074213c9","tid":2199345,"uid":7609,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-12T06:38:58.000Z","msg":"對唔住<br />\n係14億個賤種落去陪毛澤東<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed3246f2a226f232dbd10f5a498ac570186a3e7e","tid":2199345,"uid":3457,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-12T06:39:34.000Z","msg":"咩叫錯誤指控？ <br />\n係共產黨整出黎嫁wo <br />\n呀唔係 係你洩漏出黎先岩"},{"pid":"f2b575669d21cf0527dd6e0ca1d0138e844c9295","tid":2199345,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"93177df06cf95bb60c30be2773ebc92d4f5ee366","tid":2199345,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-12T06:35:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/norm